# API Arena - Core Specification

## Concepto
Plataforma educativa competitiva donde estudiantes **compiten creando APIs**. Evaluación automática mediante tests funcionales, rendimiento, diseño REST y review IA. Incluye Replay system y Multiplayer mode.

## Microservicios (todos Spring Boot + Docker)
| Servicio | Puerto | Función |
|---|---|---|
| auth-service | 8081 | JWT auth, registro, login, perfiles, grupos |
| challenge-service | 8082 | CRUD retos, featured, origin (Legacy/Community) |
| submission-service | 8083 | Submissions, orquestación del pipeline |
| sandbox-service | 8084 | Docker-in-Docker, ejecución aislada |
| testing-service | 8085 | Tests funcionales, performance, design |
| ai-review-service | 8086 | Análisis IA (Claude/GPT) — BONUS |
| leaderboard-service | 8087 | Rankings globales y por challenge |
| multiplayer-service | 8088 | Sesiones competitivas real-time — BONUS |
| metrics-service | 8089 | Estadísticas y analytics |
| notification-service | 8090 | Notificaciones push |

## Bases de datos
- **PostgreSQL**: Datos principales (users, challenges, submissions, test_results, leaderboard_entries, multiplayer_sessions, achievements, notifications, refresh_tokens, teacher_groups)
- **Redis**: Cache + sessions + rate limiting + live state
- **MongoDB**: Logs de ejecución + replay recordings
- **InfluxDB**: Métricas temporales (api_performance, container_metrics, throughput)

## Flujo principal: Submission
1. Usuario sube código → submission-service guarda + publica SUBMISSION_CREATED en Kafka
2. sandbox-service: build Docker image → lanza contenedor → publica SANDBOX_READY
3. testing-service: functional tests + performance tests + design analysis (paralelo)
4. ai-review-service (BONUS): analiza código con Claude/GPT
5. scoring: calcula total_score → actualiza submission
6. leaderboard-service: actualiza rankings → WebSocket update
7. notification-service: notifica usuario
8. sandbox-service: cleanup contenedor

## Event bus: Kafka
Comunicación asíncrona entre servicios vía eventos.

## Tiempo real: WebSocket (STOMP + SockJS)
- Updates de submission status
- Leaderboard live
- Multiplayer sync
- Notificaciones

## Roles: STUDENT, TEACHER, ADMIN

## Frontend: React 18 + React Router v6
Páginas: Landing, Login, Register, Dashboard, Challenges, ChallengeDetail, Submissions, SubmissionDetail, Leaderboard, Profile, Replay, MultiplayerHub, Teacher (Dashboard, Corrections, Groups, Challenges, CreateChallenge)

## Features BONUS
- AI Code Review (Claude/GPT)
- Replay System (grabación completa de ejecución con métricas)
- Multiplayer Mode (sesiones real-time con código único)
- Grafana dashboards embebidos
- Achievements system

## Seguridad
JWT (access + refresh), BCrypt, RBAC, rate limiting, CORS, container resource limits, network isolation, SSL/TLS.
